a-accordion-index=\"2\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"e-n-accordion-item-2591\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-header'><h3 class=\"e-n-accordion-item-title-text\"> Custom Hearing Protection <\/h3><\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class='e-n-accordion-item-title-icon'>\n\t\t\t<span class='e-opened' ><i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"far fa-angle-up\"><\/i><\/span>\n\t\t\t<span class='e-closed'><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"e-font-icon-svg e-fas-angle-down\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"><path d=\"M143 352.3L7 216.3c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9l22.6-22.6c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0l96.4 96.4 96.4-96.4c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0l22.6 22.6c9.4 9.4 9.4 24.6 0 33.9l-136 136c-9.2 9.4-24.4 9.4-33.8 0z\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span>\n\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/summary>\n\t\t\t\t<div role=\"region\" aria-labelledby=\"e-n-accordion-item-2591\" class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a5154a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4a5154a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-31bef7d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"31bef7d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>As their name suggests, custom hearing protection is made from ear impressions to provide the best fit and performance.<\/p><ul><li>Custom Earplugs &#8211; Great for musicians, workers, or everyday noise protection.<ul><li><i>Pros:<\/i> Comfortable and long-lasting.<\/li><li><i>Cons:<\/i> Requires custom fitting. Contact America&#8217;s Best Hearing to learn more about custom earplugs in Michigan, Minnesota, and Florida.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><ul><li>Impulse Filter Earplugs &#8211; Designed for hunters. Block loud gunshots while allowing softer sounds.<ul><li><i>Pros:<\/i> Smart, responsive protection.<\/li><li><i>Cons:<\/i> Best for short bursts of sound, not constant noise.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><ul><li>Sleep Plugs &#8211; Soft plugs made for side sleepers.<ul><li><i>Pros:<\/i> Comfortable and snugly fit for overnight use.<\/li><li><i>Cons:<\/i> May block important alerts like alarms.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><ul><li>In-Ear Monitors &#8211; For musicians and performers who need sound clarity on stage.<ul><li><i>Pros:<\/i> Exceptional sound quality.<\/li><li><i>Cons:<\/i> Higher cost than standard plugs.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><ul><li>SoundGear Digital Protection &#8211; Advanced digital ear protection for shooting or high-noise environments.<ul><li><i>Pros:<\/i> Reduces harmful sounds while keeping speech clear.<\/li><li><i>Cons:<\/i> Premium price.<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/details>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af44e22 elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"af44e22\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f58eaa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2f58eaa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Hearing Protection for Every Activity<\/h2><p>At America&#8217;s Best Hearing, we tailor solutions to your lifestyle:<\/p><ul><li>Hunting &#8211; Impulse filter plugs and SoundGear protect against gunfire while preserving awareness.<\/li><li>Music &#8211; Musician&#8217;s plugs and in-ear monitors reduce volume without distorting sound.<\/li><li>Swimming &#8211; Swim plugs prevent water from entering and reduce the risk of swimmer&#8217;s ear.<\/li><li>Sleeping &#8211; Sleep plugs block snoring and outside noise for better rest.<\/li><li>Work &amp; Industry &#8211; Heavy-duty plugs and earmuffs for construction, factory, or shop work.<\/li><li>Water Sports &#8211; Surf plugs protect against wind, water, and cold to prevent surfer&#8217;s ear.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-06c136e elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"06c136e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b9e5694 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b9e5694\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2>Types of Custom Ear Molds<\/h2><p>We offer ear molds in different materials for the perfect fit:<\/p><ul><li>Vinyl &#8211; Soft, flexible, and hypoallergenic. Best for children or sensitive ears.<\/li><li>Silicone &#8211; Durable, water-resistant, and flexible. Good for active users.<\/li><li>Acrylic &#8211; Hard, lightweight, and easy to clean. Durable, but less ideal for sensitive ears.<\/li><\/ul><p>Custom molds can be made for hearing aids, swimming, sleeping, or noise protection.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4abfd0f custom-accordion elementor-widget el